# ── LLM Review Engine (pick one or leave all blank for static analysis) ────────
#
# Option 1: Groq — free, fast, cloud-based (no GPU needed)
#   1. Go to https://console.groq.com/keys and sign up for free
#   2. Create an API key and paste it below
# GROQ_API_KEY=gsk_...
#
# Option 2: Ollama — fully local, no internet, no API key
#   1. Install from https://ollama.com/download
#   2. Run: ollama pull mistral   (or llama3, codellama, gemma)
#   3. Ollama is auto-detected — no config needed here
#
# Option 3: No LLM — built-in static analysis always runs as fallback

# ── Server ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# HOST=127.0.0.1
# PORT=7000

# ── Review limits ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# MAX_FILES=60
# MAX_FILE_BYTES=100000
